cb tr\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9 tinh khi\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee9ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00e2y th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 nh\u00f4m \u0111\u1eb7c, nh\u00f4m thanh, nh\u00f4m khung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i ra t\u1eeb khung nh\u00f4m, c\u1eeda nh\u00f4m x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. V\u00ec g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng pha t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t, nh\u00f4m \u0111\u00e0 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 thu mua cao.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1105\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1105\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1105\" src=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-1.jpg\" alt=\"Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1105\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u00f4m \u0111\u00e0 ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong>Ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m lo\u1ea1i 2: Nh\u00f4m d\u1ebbo\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u00f4m d\u1ebbo l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p kim nh\u00f4m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 u\u1ed1n cong linh ho\u1ea1t, th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cu\u1ed9n, t\u1ea5m v\u00e0 thanh tr\u00f2n. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh m\u1ec1m d\u1ebbo v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 gia c\u00f4ng, nh\u00f4m d\u1ebbo th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i trong nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0nh ngh\u1ec1, nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 thu mua c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 cao.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1106\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1106\" style=\"width: 600px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1106\" src=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-2.jpg\" alt=\"Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1106\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t thu mua nh\u00f4m d\u1ebbo ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><strong>Ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m lo\u1ea1i 3: M\u1ea1t nh\u00f4m\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ea1t nh\u00f4m g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c m\u1ea3nh v\u1ee5n nh\u1ecf li ti, b\u1ed9t nh\u00f4m hay ph\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m sinh ra trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gia c\u00f4ng, s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u, nh\u01b0ng khi thu gom v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn, m\u1ea1t nh\u00f4m v\u1eabn mang l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3n thu \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1107\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1107\" style=\"width: 597px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1107\" src=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-3-597x400.jpg\" alt=\"Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\" width=\"597\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-3-597x400.jpg 597w, https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-3.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 597px) 100vw, 597px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1107\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u m\u1ea1t nh\u00f4m v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><strong>C\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\u00a0<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi b\u00e1n nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb thu mua nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty l\u1edbn, uy t\u00edn, c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng thu gom v\u00e0 x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t s\u1ebd thu mua nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n hay c\u01a1 s\u1edf nh\u1ecf l\u1ebb. H\u1ecd thu mua kh\u00f4ng qua trung gian, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m chi ph\u00ed n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi tr\u1ea3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Ch\u1ee7ng lo\u1ea1i &amp; ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng g\u1ed3m nh\u00f4m \u0111\u00e0 (lo\u1ea1i 1) c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9 tinh khi\u1ebft, nh\u00f4m d\u1ebbo (lo\u1ea1i 2) gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1edd d\u1ec5 t\u00e1i ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 m\u1ea1t nh\u00f4m (lo\u1ea1i 3) c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t do c\u1ea7n qua nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng \u0111o\u1ea1n x\u1eed l\u00fd. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, gi\u00e1 thu mua s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng cao.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>V\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n xa g\u1ea7n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ra sao \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 thu mua?\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m thu mua \u0111\u1ebfn kho b\u00e3i c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m. N\u1ebfu \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed g\u1ea7n, chi ph\u00ed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ea5p, c\u00f4ng ty c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, thu mua \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch xa khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 gi\u1ea3m do ph\u00e1t sinh th\u00eam ph\u00ed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n c\u00f4ng.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>B\u00e1n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, k\u00e8m theo c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1ed1c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, b\u00e1n v\u1edbi kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf, gi\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n do chi ph\u00ed thu gom cao so v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o gi\u00e1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 thu mua nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng theo t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Khi ngu\u1ed3n cung nh\u00f4m khan hi\u1ebfm, gi\u00e1 thu mua t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, khi ngu\u1ed3n cung d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m s\u00e2u. C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt gi\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u00e1n ra \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u l\u1ee3i nhu\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1108\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1108\" style=\"width: 533px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1108\" src=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-4-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\" width=\"533\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-4-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-4.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1108\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u00e1 thu mua nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u lu\u00f4n bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng theo th\u1eddi gian<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><strong>V\u00ec sao kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t?<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m, s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 s\u1edf tr\u1ea3i d\u00e0i tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2m \u201cUy t\u00edn &#8211; Chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p &#8211; Gi\u00e1 cao\u201d Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t lu\u00f4n mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thu mua nhanh ch\u00f3ng, minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb th\u1ebf h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh th\u00e0nh ph\u00eda Nam. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh qu\u00fd b\u00e1u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c g\u1ea7n xa d\u00e0nh cho c\u00f4ng ty.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hoa h\u1ed3ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cao, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam thu nh\u1eadp cho c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c vi\u00ean.<\/li>\n<li>Quy m\u00f4 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn, ph\u1ee7 s\u00f3ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb kh\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>Thu mua nhanh trong ng\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<\/li>\n<li>Thanh to\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n ngay cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng sau khi giao d\u1ecbch ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e2n h\u00e0ng uy t\u00edn, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eadn n\u01a1i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_1109\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-1109\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-1109\" src=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-5-535x400.jpg\" alt=\"Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m\" width=\"535\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-5-535x400.jpg 535w, https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhom-5.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 535px) 100vw, 535px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1109\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c thu mua nh\u00f4m ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t, c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 thu mua. V\u1edbi uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng, thu mua t\u1eadn n\u01a1i v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn hoa h\u1ed3ng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cao!<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t \u0111ang thu mua:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"69\" data-end=\"151\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"71\" data-end=\"151\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-dong\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"71\" data-end=\"151\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"315\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"237\" data-end=\"315\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-sat\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"237\" data-end=\"315\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u s\u1eaft<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"316\" data-end=\"398\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"318\" data-end=\"398\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-nhua\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"318\" data-end=\"398\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u1ef1a<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"399\" data-end=\"481\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"481\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-inox\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"481\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u inox<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"482\" data-end=\"562\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"562\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-vai\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"484\" data-end=\"562\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"563\" data-end=\"651\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"651\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/thu-mua-phe-lieu-hop-kim\/\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"565\" data-end=\"651\">Thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u h\u1ee3p kim<\/a><\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Minh Khang Ph\u00e1t chuy\u00ean thu mua ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u nh\u00f4m gi\u00e1 cao, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u1eadn n\u01a1i nhanh ch\u00f3ng, uy t\u00edn v\u00e0 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c chi\u1ebft kh\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, thanh to\u00e1n nhanh v\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 minh b\u1ea1ch, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n ph\u1ebf li\u1ec7u [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1110,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[70],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1104","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-dich-vu"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1104","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1104"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1104\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1169,"href":"https:\/\/phelieuminhkhangphat.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2